article.headline: Bailey scores 23 and Incarnate Word takes down Western Illinois 86-75
article.description: — Davion Bailey scored 23 points as Incarnate Word beat Western Illinois 86-75 on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Bailey scores 23 and Incarnate Word takes down Western Illinois 86-75
article.story: MOBILE, Ala. -- — Davion Bailey scored 23 points as Incarnate Word beat Western Illinois 86-75 on Wednesday night. Bailey shot 8 for 15, including 6 for 12 from beyond the arc for the Cardinals (4-3). Jalin Anderson scored 18 points and added eight assists. Dylan Hayman finished with 17 points. The Leathernecks (4-4) were led by Marko Maletic, who recorded 23 points. Kayden Carter added 13 points and seven rebounds for Western Illinois. Julius Rollins finished with 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
